<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Manufacturing | DGT</title>
    <link href="index.css"  rel="stylesheet" >
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/aos/2.3.4/aos.css">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/6.4.2/css/all.min.css">
    <script src="https://kit.fontawesome.com/a076d05399.js"></script>
    <script src="https://cdn.tailwindcss.com"></script>
    <script src="/search.js"></script>
<link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/swiper@11/swiper-bundle.min.css" />
<script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/swiper@11/swiper-bundle.min.js"></script>
<script src="/Aos.js"></script>
    <style>
        * {
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            box-sizing: border-box;
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
        }

        /* Hero Section */
        .hero {
            position: relative;
            height: 80vh;
            background: url('images/manufacturing.jpg') no-repeat center center/cover;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
        }

        .hero-content {
            background-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.4);
            padding: 30px;
            text-align: center;
            border-radius: 10px;
            max-width: 600px;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 6px rgba(16, 15, 15, 0.2);
        }

        .hero-content h1 {
    font-size: 2.5rem;
    color: #f7f2f2;
    text-shadow: -1px -1px 0 #000, 1px -1px 0 #000, -1px 1px 0 #000, 1px 1px 0 #000 !important;
}


        .hero-content p {
            font-size: 1.2rem;
            color: #fdf7f7;
             text-shadow: -1px -1px 0 #000, 1px -1px 0 #000, -1px 1px 0 #000, 1px 1px 0 #000 !important;
            margin-top: 10px;
        }

        .container {
            width: 90%;
            max-width: 1200px;
            margin: auto;
            padding: 50px 0;
        }

        .manufacturing-section {
            margin-bottom: 50px;
            text-align: center;
        }

        .manufacturing-section h2 {
            font-size: 2rem;
            color: #333;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }

        .manufacturing-section p {
            font-size: 1.1rem;
            color: #555;
            max-width: 800px;
            margin: 0 auto;
        }

        .grid {
            display: flex;
            flex-wrap: wrap;
            gap: 20px;
            justify-content: center;
            margin-top: 30px;
        }

        .mf-card {
            background: #f9f9f9;
            padding: 20px;
            border-radius: 8px;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 6px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
            flex: 1 1 calc(50% - 20px);
            min-width: 300px;
            text-align: center;
        }

        .mf-card h3 {
            color: #ff9100;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
        }

        .tools {
            background: #f1f1f1;
            padding: 30px;
            border-radius: 8px;
            margin-top: 20px;
            text-align: center;
        }

        .cta {
            text-align: center;
            margin-top: 50px;
        }

        .cta-footer a {
            display: inline-block;
            padding: 15px 30px;
            background: #e67009;
            color: white;
            text-decoration: none;
            border-radius: 5px;
            font-size: 1.2rem;
        }

        @media (max-width: 768px) {
            .grid {
                flex-direction: column;
            }

            .mf-card {
                flex: 1 1 100%;
            }
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
     <%- include('partials/navbar') %>
    <section class="hero">
        <div class="hero-content" data-aos="zoom-out"  data-aos-delay="100">
            <h1>Manufacturing</h1>
            <p>Optimizing production processes through AI-powered automation and real-time data insights.</p>
        </div>
    </section>

    <div class="container" data-aos="fade-up"  data-aos-delay="100">
        <section class="manufacturing-section">
            <h2>Revolutionizing Manufacturing with AI</h2>
            <p>AI-driven solutions are transforming the manufacturing industry by enhancing operational efficiency, automating production, and improving real-time monitoring. DGT's AI-powered analytics and automation optimize production lines, reduce downtime, and boost productivity.</p>
        </section>

        <section class="manufacturing-section">
            <h2>Key AI-Powered Solutions</h2>
            <div class="grid" data-aos-delay="100">
                <div class="mf-card" data-aos="fade-up">
                    <h3>Smart Production Planning</h3>
                    <p>AI-powered demand forecasting and real-time scheduling for optimized production.</p>
                </div>
                <div class="mf-card" data-aos="fade-up" data-aos-delay="100">
                    <h3>Predictive Maintenance</h3>
                    <p>Advanced AI models to predict machinery failures and reduce downtime.</p>
                </div>
                <div class="mf-card"  data-aos="fade-up" data-aos-delay="100">
                    <h3>Shop Floor Analytics</h3>
                    <p>Real-time AI analytics to monitor production performance and efficiency.</p>
                </div>
                <div class="mf-card"  data-aos="fade-up" data-aos-delay="100">
                    <h3>Supply Chain Optimization</h3>
                    <p>AI-driven logistics and procurement for cost efficiency and reduced lead times.</p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </section>

        <section class="manufacturing-section tools"data-aos="fade-up" data-aos-delay="100">
            <h2>Technology Stack</h2>
            <p><strong>Salesforce Manufacturing Cloud</strong> | <a href="/celonis">Celonis</a> | Power BI | CI/CD Tools</p>
        </section>

        <section class="manufacturing-section cta-footer" data-aos="fade-down" data-aos-delay="100">
            <h2>Drive Manufacturing Excellence with AI</h2>
            <a href="/contactus">Contact Us</a>
        </section>
    </div>
    <script>
        AOS.init({
                  duration: 1000,
                  once: true,
              });
  </script>
</body>
</html>
